Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just supposed to be an ordinary third grader,\Nbut a sudden encounter changed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was given a red jewel from which\N I gained magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My unexpected encounter has set two things in\N motion, which are slowly building in intensity:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My intertwined feelings, and the beginning of this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was when magic would first\N begin to change my ordinary life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:01:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always so uneasy that I was shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hugging my knees in the corner of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid of knowing the "truth"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and closed the door to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through a kind lie, I discovered where I should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fled and took refuge in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows of the lonely sea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,being dyed a deep blue color
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that hides my loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With wholehearted feelings, I wounded your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret within your eyes makes me want to soak it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the truth behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your smile with a warm love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I touch it, the warmth that seems so breakable will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,break away from its past and overflow.\NBecause you're always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will no longer be puzzled over the shadow of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with this outfit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My magical incantation is "lyrical"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.08,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our magical device uses a "programming"\N system that lets our magic take form.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in order to make that system work,\Nits user needs to provide spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing was born from the source of disgusting and\N abominable power, and took that form to protect itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make it stop, you need to seal it with your\N staff and return it to its original form.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand, but how do I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you did before was one of your two types\N of magic: attacking and defending.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're basic forms of magic you activate\N by wishing with all your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in order to summon enough power to\N fully stop it, you'll need an incantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incantation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no doubt that an incantation will come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.33,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyrical Magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you attack and seal it correctly,\N it should change back into a Jewel Seed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jewel Seed, Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:51.05,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Mode, Set Up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.66,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by, Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyrical Magical. Jewel Seed Serial XXI!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.06,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Jewel Seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touch it with Raising Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:48.91,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Receipt Number XXI.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you all right? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm seen here, I might get in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For now, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I woke you up? Sorry for being so rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now. I'm pretty much recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Most of the wounds you\N had have vanished. That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you helped me out, I was able to use my\N remaining magical power to help heal myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it okay if we formally introduce ourselves now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Takamachi Nanoha.\N A third-grade elementary school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My close friends and family call me Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yuuno Scrya. Scrya is my family name,\N so Yuuno's my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuno-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I've gotten you involved in this, Nanoha-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I think I'm okay with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:08:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I forgot. Yuuno-kun, you're still a little\N hurt, so you won't be able to rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's go back to my house.\N We can sort the other things out afterwards, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just where have you been at this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... that is... uh... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You look pretty down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess, you were worried and\N went to check on him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... uh, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't understand how you feel, but I still\N can't believe you snuck out of the house like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Nanoha's a good girl,\N so she won't do this again. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Onii-chan... I'm sorry for sneaking\N out and worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there we are. Everything's all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, it sure is cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Mom will think it's so cute\N and faint when she first sees it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say the probability of that is pretty high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, Good morning, Yuuno-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for now, I'll say good job at\N making it through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Last night, when I showed Yuuno-kun\N to Mom and Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is such a cutie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Please take it easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cuuuute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,425)}It certainly looks like a smart, long rodent, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called a "ferret," Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it can do any tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is a cool little smart guy, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there was a big fuss for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, we discussed what to do for Yuuno-kun's\N meals, and the whole fuss over him started again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, the two of us didn't really\N get to talk much last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you used to calling me by my first name yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We only managed to get used to calling\N each other by our first names...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and to start talking like friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get to school, so let me hear all about what's\N going on with you when I get home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we're apart, we can still talk to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're a mage now, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is like when you first called to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. We can talk as long as\N you have the Raising Heart with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now try talking to me with your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. It's easy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll tell you about a lot of things whenever you're free.\N Like about me, magic, and the Jewel Seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyrical Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha! Did you hear about\N what happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vet we went to yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there was a car accident or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they said the wall was smashed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been worried about the ferret...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.05,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,So he's safe at your house, Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But that's one incredible coincidence, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:27.48,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,To have met him on the street when\N he was escaping from that mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:28.56,Default,A+S,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:34.81,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not a lie! It's not a lie!\N I've only slightly tweaked the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:42.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like my family doesn't\N mind having a pet ferret...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:45.29,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,...so we're going to be taking care\N of him at my house for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.12,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just have to come up with a name for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.16,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided on one yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.91,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. His name is Yuuno-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.91,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.52,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Yuuno-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:02.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,As I told you before, some kanji are formed\N by using the "hen" and "tsukuri" radicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:08.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,By combining these radicals, each kanji can hold many\N different meanings, even if made of just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is because each hen radical\N has some meaning by itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,...and each of the tsukuri radicals also have meanings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:16.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,For example, to write the word "person,"\N you only have to use the ninben radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,To write out the word "water,"\N you use the sanzui radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:21.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And when writing out "wood,"\N you use the kihen radical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, why don't I give you a short quiz on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.31,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Using these three hen radicals, what other words can\N you think of by combining them with a tsukiru radical?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:30.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Jewel Seeds are ancient relics of my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:37.67,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Originally, they were magical stones which could grant\N the wishes of those who possessed them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:42.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...sometimes the manifestations of their power\N become unstable, like what happened last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:46.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, they'll turn on the stone's user and devour\N everything in the area, including the user's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:59.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are times when people will misuse them and get\N confused, which can also cause them to run wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.98,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So why was something so dangerous\N in my neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:11.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On my home world, I'm an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:14.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And one day, I discovered something\N in an old rock formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:18.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sent a team of investigators to claim\N it and put it into safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:23.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the ship that was taking it away had some\N sort of accident, and there was a big disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:37.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Twenty-one Jewel Seeds were scattered\N across this world because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:41.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we've only managed to find two so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.96,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So there's another nineteen left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.17,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:54.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, don't you think your balsam\N plants have grown a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many centimeters they've grown?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... maybe two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's definitely grown three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:01.55,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? But wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:08.67,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From what you've told me so far, it's not really your\N fault the Jewel Seeds got scattered here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:12.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I was the one who first found them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:17.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I have to find them all,\N and return them to where they should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:24.90,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow... somehow, I can relate to your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:28.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sure are a diligent person, aren't you, Yuuno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:35.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Have you all been filling out the surveys and\N reading the caution forms correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:39.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly hope so, because if you mix up what's\N a weed and what isn't, it'll be quite a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:45.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, please don't forget to write your name,\N the date, and how much it grew on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:52.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm terribly sorry about getting you involved last\N night and making you help me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:58.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like to stay in your care for a while longer\N as I rest and let my magical powers return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:03.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a week... no, if I had just five days, all of my power\N would return, so if I could stay with you until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If your powers do return, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:11.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll leave to search for the rest of\N the Jewel Seeds alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.41,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-You won't allow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:22.60,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible for me to help you during normal school\N and cram school, but I can help you out any other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:25.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it'll be dangerous, like last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:36.22,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, we've already become acquainted,\N and I've heard you entire story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:38.26,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just can't leave you alone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.31,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if people in the neighborhood are going\N to keep running into things like last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.90,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it'll be a problem for everyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:50.35,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuuno-kun, you don't have anyone to help\N you out when you're alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:54.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being all alone is sad. Let me help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:03.33,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"If someone's in need and you\N have the power to help them..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.63,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"...you should never hesitate to help them."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.13,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At least, that's what my dad taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:19.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You seem pretty troubled, and I can\N help you with my strength, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.60,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With my magical power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:30.53,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though I don't know if I can become a proper mage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,440)}Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.03,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\pos(320,470)}You're already a great mage, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:37.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure you have an incredible amount\N of talent, more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:43.73,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}R-Really? I don't really get it yet myself...\N but for now, teach me what you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:45.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:48.22,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'll do my best, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:56.02,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now then, I'll be back at the house any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.80,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How about we eat some snacks\N together when I get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, yeah... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:05.23,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what kind of snacks we should have today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:17.76,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.82,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuuno-kun, what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new Jewel Seed has been activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:23.83,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:28.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's stand up against it together. Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha, the Raising Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.61,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:02.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It possessed an animal that was in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:04.37,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,W-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot tougher when it has a stable form like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.88,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine... probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:15.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Activate the Raising Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.34,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! How do I activate it again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:27.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Start from "I, the one who accepted this\N mission!" The activation password!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.61,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember that whole long thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you again, so just repeat after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:36.11,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:51.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raising... Heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:53.84,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by, Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:55.21,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:10.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She activated the Raising Heart\N without even saying the password...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha! Your protective clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.15,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier Jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:29.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.19,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Condition: All green.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She took no damage from that impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:05.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought, this girl has an\N incredible amount of talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:08.83,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... it didn't really hurt as much as I thought it would...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.08,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... all I have to do now is seal it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:15.29,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raising Heart, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:16.63,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.20,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.30,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.15,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by, Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:41.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Lyrical Magical. Jewel Seed Serial XVI!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:43.75,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:46.32,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:09.89,Raising Heart,RH,0000,0000,0000,,Receipt Number XVI.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:13.43,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's all right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:14.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:17.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much else we have to do now, like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:30.65,Default,P,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I wonder if I tripped and hit my head...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:42.61,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Good job... I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:45.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'd say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:53.72,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first day I, Takamachi Nanoha, started\N out as a magical girl had finally ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:57.05,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've made a new friend, Yuuno-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:23:01.36,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know much about him, magic,\N or the dangers that will be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:04.15,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, a whole lot has happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:06.82,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I sure am hungry from all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:13.01,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess for now, I just have to keep doing my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. I was stumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and losing my way on my journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since you were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.60,0:23:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the silver wind came looking for\N two who were lacking something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:24:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beyond the cellophane sea and forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.10,0:24:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was just crying in our city that's\N nothing more than a diorama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.61,0:24:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you held out to me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the ever-swaying years,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.07,0:24:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt you looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.75,0:24:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I had finally, finally found the secret key.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.08,0:24:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. Gather the lemon-colored
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.02,0:24:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drops of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.66,0:24:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to gently light the path you're walking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.65,0:24:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish, even if it's a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.57,0:24:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you can't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.19,0:24:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then remember that because you were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.02,0:25:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.78,0:25:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Somehow through everything,\N I've become a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.77,0:25:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I've had to do this and that\N as a magical girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.03,0:25:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}...and I'm really excited about it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.24,0:25:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I'm still Takamachi Nanoha but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}These kind of problems\N have to come first!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.50,0:25:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Next time there'll be a problem\N that involves the entire town!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.75,0:25:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}This is looking really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.38,0:25:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Next time on\N Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.56,0:25:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Episode Three:\NThe Town's in a Lot of Danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.58,0:25:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I, Lyrical Magical,\N will do my best!
